    <briefdescription>
<para>Initializer that configures spawned entities with random direction. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1behavior_1_1initializers_1_1RandomDirectionInitializer" kindref="compound">RandomDirectionInitializer</ref> generates a random 2D direction and applies it to the entity&apos;s DirectionComponent and Move2DComponent. This is useful for spawning enemies that should move in unpredictable directions.</para>
<para>Components affected:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>**DirectionComponent:** Sets random normalized direction</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>**Move2DComponent:** Sets move intent in the random direction</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Uses a static Random generator with a fixed seed for reproducibility.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1behavior_1_1SpawnInitializer" kindref="compound">SpawnInitializer</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
